                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <h2>Monitor compliance</h2>
                        <p>Choose to execute policies or audit policy compliance targeting best practices. View policy compliance for all policies, or aggregate multiple policies into a plan and supervise compliance for the entire plan.</p>
                    </div>
